## ✨ Features

AgroTech bridges the gap between traditional farming and modern technology by leveraging **Real-time IoT Data** and **Generative AI** for predictive farming insights.

### 🎯 Core Capabilities

| Feature                | Description                                               | Status    |
| ---------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- | --------- |
| 🌡️ **IoT Monitoring** | Real-time Soil Moisture, Temperature, and Humidity stats  | ✅ Active |
| 🤖 **AI Crop Advisor** | Gemini-powered suggestions for fertilizers and pesticides | ✅ Active |
| 💧 **Auto-Irrigation** | Automatic water pump control based on soil moisture levels| ✅ Active |
| 🌦️ **Weather Forecast**| Integrated weather API for advanced harvest planning      | ✅ Active |
| 📈 **Yield Analytics** | Data visualization for seasonal growth and crop health    | ✅ Active |
| 🛒 **Direct Market** | Platform for farmers to list produce directly to buyers   | 🏗️ WIP    |

### 🛠️ The Smart Farming Workflow
📡 Sensors → ☁️ Cloud Data → 🤖 AI Analysis → 📱 Farmer Insights → 💧 Automated Action

- **📡 IoT Sensing**: ESP32/Arduino sensors send soil and environmental data to the Node.js backend.
- **🤖 Gemini AI Integration**: The system analyzes sensor data trends and provides "Natural Language" advice to farmers (e.g., *"Soil nitrogen is low; consider organic composting."*)
- **⚡ Remote Control**: Farmers can toggle irrigation systems manually via the React dashboard from anywhere.

