## 📁 Project Structure

```bash
📦 AgroTech
├── 📂 Hardware/               # Arduino/ESP32 C++ Code for sensors
├── 🌐 Backend/                # Node.js & Express (IoT Data Processing)
│   ├── 🤖 controllers/       # AI logic & Sensor data handlers
│   ├── 💾 models/            # Mongoose Schemas (SensorData, User, Crop)
│   └── 📜 server.js
│
├── ⚛️ Frontend/               # React.js (Dashboard & Visualization)
│   ├── 📁 src/
│   │   ├── 🧩 components/    # Real-time Gauges, Charts, AI Chatbot
│   │   └── 📄 pages/         # Dashboard, Analytics, Field Map
│
├── 📖 README.md
└── 📄 LICENSE

